    <title type="html"><![CDATA[replace disqus with youyan]]></title>
    <link href="http://zhangchunlei.com/blog/2015/11/24/replace-discus-with-youyan/"/>
    <updated>2015-11-24T09:43:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://zhangchunlei.com/blog/2015/11/24/replace-discus-with-youyan</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>将jiathis的喜欢按钮以及分享按钮放在sharing.html文件末尾。<br/>
将友言的代码放在share_comment.html文件中（source/<em>includes/post/share_comment.html），并通过disqus（source/</em>includes/disqus.html）加载，也就是在这个文件中加入下面的代码。</p>

<pre><code>
<!-- JiaThis Button -->
  
    <!-- JiaThis share Button BEGIN -->
<div class="jiathis_style_32x32">
	<a class="jiathis_button_qzone"></a>
	<a class="jiathis_button_tsina"></a>
	<a class="jiathis_button_tqq"></a>
	<a class="jiathis_button_weixin"></a>
	<a class="jiathis_button_renren"></a>
	<a href="http://www.jiathis.com/share?uid=2072381" class="jiathis jiathis_txt jtico jtico_jiathis" target="_blank"></a>
	<a class="jiathis_counter_style"></a>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
var jiathis_config = {data_track_clickback:'true'};
</script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://v3.jiathis.com/code/jia.js?uid=2072381" charset="utf-8"></script>
<!-- JiaThis Button END -->


<!-- JiaThis like Button BEGIN -->
<div class="jiathis_style">
	<a class="jiathis_like_tsina" data="width=120"></a>
	<a class="jiathis_like_qzone"></a>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://v3.jiathis.com/code_mini/jia.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
<!-- JiaThis Button END -->


<!-- UY BEGIN -->
<div id="uyan_frame"></div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://v2.uyan.cc/code/uyan.js?uid=2072381"></script>
<!-- UY END -->

  
</code></pre>


<p>别忘了自觉去掉/</p>

<p>当然需要在_config.yml中添加开关：</p>

<pre><code>
#jiathis
comment_share: true
</code></pre>


<p>修改_layouts中post.html文件中sharing的位置，将其放在上一篇和下一篇博文导航条的后面。</p>

<p>友言网的验证<br/>
这个不需要操心，现在已经能自动验证了，应该是凭借ID号。</p>
